-- Baosteel, Hebei Interested in Thyssen’s Brazil Plant, FTD Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-06-20T18:05:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/baosteel-hebei-interested-in-thyssen-s-brazil-plant-ftd-says.html
China ’s Baosteel Group Corp. and
Hebei Iron & Steel Co. Ltd have showed interest in a possible
purchase of a  ThyssenKrupp AG (TKA) ’s steel plant in  Brazil , the
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported in a preview of an article
that will run tomorrow, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
